repositorio_dir = os.path.dirname(os.path.realpath(__file__))
file_name = os.path.join(repositorio_dir, 'listasview.html')
fn = open(file_name, 'r')
text = fn.read()
fn.close()
s = ListView(text)
s.extract_table()
s.get_max_length()
self.assertEqual(len(s.max_column), 4)
s.print_table()
self.assertEqual(len(s.data), 23)
